Package lgp.core.program

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Output<TData>
    Represents the output of a class Program.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Outputs
    A collection of built-in interface Output implementations.
    Program<TData,TOutput extends Output<TData>>
    An LGP program that is composed of instructions that operate on registers.
    ProgramGenerator<TProgram,TOutput extends Output<TProgram>>
    Generates class Program instances to be used in an LGP population.
    ProgramTranslator<TProgram,TOutput extends Output<TProgram>>
    Module that can be used to translate programs to external representations.
